Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}于是 太阳系行星之间的微粒{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And then the particles that live in the solar system between the planets{\r}
